          "description": "I was super impressed with this CityMD location!! I was seen very quickly, the intake person at the front desk was efficient and helpful, and the PA and attendant who took my vitals were outstanding. I saw the PA called Alyssa and she was absolutely fantastic. I was very distressed because a piece of my hearing aid was stuck in my ear and everyone was very patient with me even though I was freaked out. Alyssa was very quick about getting it out quickly and being very reassuring. She is amazing. I love this location!! I highly recommend it!",
