          "description": "Honestly not sure why the reviews are so bad\u2026 made me skeptical as well. I sprained my ankle badly playing basketball and wanted to get it checked out. Minimal wait time and all in all took about 30 minutes. Got a couple x rays and a helpful explanation from the doctor who referred me to a specialist for a small fracture. Price of all this honestly came in under what I was expecting as well. Would recommend if in need of urgent care + x rays.",
