          "description": "I am very grateful that CityMd is always available when I need medical care  as it takes weeks or months to get an appointment with my primary care physician. Their physicians are consistently competent, empathetic, and reassuring when you need them. The doctor I saw on Friday whose name I don't remember was wonderful and  helped me deal with a difficult situation that day .",
