          "description": "I highly recommend this service. The doctor was very professional, polite and made me feel comfortable. After an examination, and minor treatment, he recommended that I get a CT scan of the area of my injury (head injury) which I did. All is well and I am grateful that I took his advice.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkRWN6bFBjWEZ1VVdaTWVISm5NWFpGTmtaWlRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xb0b350462f6165b6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOldEczlPcXFuUWZMeHJnMXZFNkZZTmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
